.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, cola, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, skydiving, fishing, collecting
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, climbing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | hot-chocolate      | sprite       | cola   |
| Hobby      | camping   | skydiving  | collecting | fishing     |
| Sport      | water-polo     | snowboarding | climbing        | rowing |

