.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, banana, zucchini, grapefruit
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, dancing, filmmaking, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, surfing, water-polo, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person eating banana##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
6. the person eating banana is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating zucchini##2
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | zucchini | banana  | nectarine | grapefruit      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | writing  | sudoku | dancing |
| Sport   | parkour | tennis | surfing | water-polo     |

