The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, disaster, satire, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skiing, soccer, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching satire movies##2
7. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | grapes  | cauliflower    | broccoli | kale  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | fantasy       | disaster        | martial-arts    |
| Sport         | skiing | ice-hockey | cricket  | soccer |

