.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, chess, baking, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, animation, adventure, family
4 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, hedgehog, snake
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is chess##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | video-games  | chess | baking | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | family | animation   | adventure         |
| Pet           | fish | hedgehog  | mouse   | snake      |

