2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating lemon##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the person eating carrot##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating peas##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the fan of country and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | peas  | lemon    | garlic | carrot       |
| Hobby         | video-games | filmmaking | baking  | reading |
| Music-Genre   | country   | metal      | punk  | jazz     |

