1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the owner of the ferret is the person eating banana##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the owner of the rabbit and the person eating asparagus##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the pony##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the bird##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | asparagus  | nectarine | grapes | banana     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | collecting   | rock-climbing  | baking    |
| Pet     | bird        | pony       | rabbit      | ferret |

