4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea     | cola | fanta       |
| Hobby      | camping  | fishing | reading  | dancing |
| Pet        | hamster  | snake      | horse        | fish      |

