The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, family, musical, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, subway, helicopter
1. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the subway is the architect##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the photographer##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is between the person watching musical movies and the architect##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
