.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, filmmaking, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, designer, teacher, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, surfing, lacrosse, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the social-worker##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is between the doctor and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
6. the teacher is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | filmmaking   | traveling           | card-games         | reading      |
| Job     | doctor | teacher | social-worker | designer |
| Sport   | lacrosse     | surfing         | cycling       | volleyball        |

