.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, fanta, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, techno, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, indonesian, turkish, argentine
1. the fan of blues is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking fanta and the indonesian##2
3. the person drinking fanta is the fan of folk##1
4. the person drinking fanta is between the fan of techno and the argentine##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the pakistani is between the turkish and the fan of indie##2
7. the fan of blues is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta | coffee   | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | folk    | techno   | indie     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | turkish | pakistani | indonesian   |

