.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, lemonade, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: avocado, peas, pumpkin, tomato
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, biathlon, skateboarding, cycling
1. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
5. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | water    | sprite | almond-milk           | lemonade |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin    | peas          | tomato   |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | biathlon   | cycling | soccer  |

