4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, guinea-pig, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, scooter, ship
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the ship is the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the rat is between the person eating lemon and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | lemon | orange | cucumber | pear |
| Pet         | rabbit       | rat     | guinea-pig   | chinchilla   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | taxi | scooter | ship |

 